<title>牛！这位85后获得全球最高几何奖！</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/fezhnh8CWW</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/fezhnh8CWW</guid>
<description>&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; px=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; caret-color:=&quot;&quot; text-size-adjust:=&quot;&quot; auto=&quot;&quot; em=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;根据美国数学会11月19日日官网消息，三年一度的美国数学会维布伦几何奖得主宣布，获奖者为，陈秀雄、西蒙·唐纳森、孙崧，表彰他们通过在2015年在《美国数学会杂志》发表的三篇系列论文“法诺流形上的卡勒-爱因斯坦度量”I、II、III，解决了一个在微分几何领域长期存在的猜想。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; px=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; caret-color:=&quot;&quot; text-size-adjust:=&quot;&quot; auto=&quot;&quot; em=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5544444444444444&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;900&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ge3XF3ILx3ibl3ich3GHrmsrOv6NVajbxy9Vo39Yy7DmxyoAJUAqia2a04TuMJVuLmMeYt43WUcNsWwzkmxBzjQBw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; px=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; caret-color:=&quot;&quot; text-size-adjust:=&quot;&quot; auto=&quot;&quot; em=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;很巧的是，陈秀雄、孙崧本科都就读于中国科技大学。而后者赴美深造时，其导师就是陈秀雄教授。这次师徒一起获奖，可喜可贺。&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; px=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; caret-color:=&quot;&quot; text-size-adjust:=&quot;&quot; auto=&quot;&quot; em=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; px=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; caret-color:=&quot;&quot; text-size-adjust:=&quot;&quot; auto=&quot;&quot; em=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.805&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;400&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ge3XF3ILx3ibl3ich3GHrmsrOv6NVajbxyfQndicAec0WXqkrXyZkuMeb5WAkvGcrNkLfWfMLebG5icI533E7ibUj2g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; px=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; caret-color:=&quot;&quot; text-size-adjust:=&quot;&quot; auto=&quot;&quot; em=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; px=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;本次获奖者孙崧特别值得一提，这位据称出生于1986年的年轻学者，曾于2000年以怀宁县第一名的成绩考入怀宁中学，2002年，正在读高二的他获得全国高中学生化学竞赛二等奖，同年参加高考，顺利考入中科大少年班，成为该县考进科大少年班的第一人。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

